The cost-effectiveness of seven behavioural interventions to prevent drug misuse 
in vulnerable populations.

Pennington B(1), Collins B(2), Leigh S(3), Martin AP(4), Owen L(5), Fischer 
A(6), Sumnall H(7), Bates G(8).

Author information:
(1)Centre for Guidelines, National Institute for Health and Care Excellence, 
