Are Differences in Disability-Free Life Expectancy by Gender, Race, and 
Education Widening at Older Ages?

Solé-Auró A(1), Beltrán-Sánchez H(2), Crimmins EM(3).

Author information:
(1)Ined- Institut National d'Études Démographiques, 133 boulevard Davout, 75980 
